documentation.author: Terry Wright
documentation.purpose: Automatically add an Active, Confirmed, Medical PE - Pulmonary embolism problem to patient's problem list if any Physician or MLP position adds a related ICD9 code as Admitting, Final or Discharge and the patient does not already have a similar Active Medical problem.
documentation.explanation: Rule triggers upon a diagnosis event. Diagnosis type needs to be either Admitting, Discharge or Final. Rule will enter a PE - Pulmonary embolism problem with the Confirmation = Confirmed, Classification = Medical, Status = Active.
